    "long_description": "The Crossroads Arts District comes alive after dark, offering one of Kansas City's most eclectic and walkable bar scenes. Start the evening at Green Lady Lounge, an intimate jazz and cocktail bar with a cool retro vibe. Around the corner, Swordfish Tom's pours some of the most carefully crafted cocktails in the city in a moody, speakeasy-style setting. For something tropical, Kon Tiki brings tiki bar energy to a cozy basement room. Up-Down KC blends nostalgia and nightlife with classic arcade games and cold beer under one roof. Close out the night at The Wise Guy, a neighborhood Italian restaurant and bar with a laid-back, neighborhood feel. The whole loop is barely a half-mile — easy to cover on foot.",
